  "root_text": {
    "iti31:0.1": "Itivuttaka 31 ",
    "iti31:0.2": "Dukanipāta ",
    "iti31:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti31:0.4": "Atapanīyasutta ",
    "iti31:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti31:2.1": "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā atapanīyā. ",
    "iti31:2.2": "Katame dve? ",
    "iti31:2.3": "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco katakalyāṇo hoti, katakusalo, katabhīruttāṇo, akatapāpo, akataluddo, akatakibbiso. ",
    "iti31:2.4": "So ‘kataṁ me kalyāṇan’tipi na tappati, ‘akataṁ me pāpan’tipi na tappati. ",
    "iti31:2.5": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā atapanīyā”ti. ",
    "iti31:2.6": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti31:2.7": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti31:3.1": "“Kāyaduccaritaṁ hitvā, ",
    "iti31:3.2": "vacīduccaritāni ca; ",
    "iti31:3.3": "Manoduccaritaṁ hitvā, ",
    "iti31:3.4": "yañcaññaṁ dosasañhitaṁ. ",
    "iti31:4.1": "Akatvākusalaṁ kammaṁ, ",
    "iti31:4.2": "katvāna kusalaṁ bahuṁ; ",
    "iti31:4.3": "Kāyassa bhedā sappañño, ",
    "iti31:4.4": "saggaṁ so upapajjatī”ti. ",
    "iti31:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti31:5.2": "Catutthaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti31:0.1": "So It Was Said 31 ",
    "iti31:0.2": "The Book of the Twos ",
    "iti31:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti31:0.4": "Not Mortifying ",
    "iti31:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti31:2.1": "“These two things, mendicants, are not mortifying. ",
    "iti31:2.2": "What two? ",
    "iti31:2.3": "It’s when someone has done good and skillful things that keep them safe, but has not done bad things, violence and sin. ",
    "iti31:2.4": "Thinking, ‘I have done good things’, they’re not mortified. Thinking, ‘I haven’t done bad things’, they’re not mortified. ",
    "iti31:2.5": "These are the two things that are not mortifying.” ",
    "iti31:2.6": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti31:2.7": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti31:3.1": "“Having given up bad conduct ",
    "iti31:3.2": "by way of body, ",
    "iti31:3.3": "speech, and mind, ",
    "iti31:3.4": "and whatever else is corrupt; ",
    "iti31:4.1": "not having done bad deeds, ",
    "iti31:4.2": "and having done many good, ",
    "iti31:4.3": "when their body breaks up, that wise person ",
    "iti31:4.4": "is reborn in heaven.” ",
    "iti31:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
